{"tid":1163940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都有性單戀","createTime":"2019-05-20T17:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T06:13:11.000Z","uid":200718,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"285a4e80b3fa2683ddfe327d0693f0a3e29967dc","tid":1163940,"uid":200718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"性單戀即係話當你鍾意一個人而對方鍾意返你嘅時候，個份鍾意嘅感覺就會減退，甚至變做反感。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前有兩段關係明明可以好好發展，但最後因爲我feel 到自己唔再鍾意對方而無疾而終左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來升左上U，又遇到一個好好嘅男仔，本身都對佢有好感但知道左佢都對我有意思之後我又feel到自己對佢熱度退減。我好想知自己係咪有個心理關口衝破唔到所以想試下同佢發展，可能衝破左就會變返正常人。但同時我又好驚最後不歡而散，晒大家時間又hurt左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f4d2c9f1d64e41b8b16cce59c78fad2f04b37f","tid":1163940,"uid":254259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f5c36f92313e4bacdcdf07a027446639a5e3f65","tid":1163940,"uid":237497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"SM<br />\nare you M？"},{"pid":"7b45cb9925637a19a9fc587c1f8277846060f9a0","tid":1163940,"uid":200718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0f4d2c9f1d64e41b8b16cce59c78fad2f04b37f","tid":1163940,"uid":254259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"冇咁嘅資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acc6dcc4b612ac0f5c413cd51deeca70d87e407","tid":1163940,"uid":73066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"唔拍永遠唔會知自己想要咩<br />\n或者你地會一齊好耐唔會hurt到人<br />\n亦有可能你真係唔岩feel<br />\n拍完幾個月就散<br />\n無人知<br />\n但當下你意識驚就好大機會剩下發生既事跟你既想法一樣<br />\n取決於你有幾大衝動想衝破關口"},{"pid":"1372c449f843d86d11708e5d6671e39d7273010e","tid":1163940,"uid":200718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score